{"tid":1813233,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在","createTime":"2020-01-06T06:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T09:14:59.000Z","uid":304769,"like":75,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7777d94a125add9f14e3d94d901b39d25720a61b","tid":1813233,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:27:46.000Z","msg":"從中國銀行支持送中，到交通銀行炒末日博士羅家聰，足以看到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中資尤其國企的險惡本質，他們的本質就是共產黨，只不過掛上不同招牌而已</span></strong>。而他們的任務就是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將香港一切經濟利益、外匯、職位空缺全面送中，另外借助在商界影響力進行白色恐怖、操控選舉、噤聲、打壓香港人</span></strong>。而出賣香港人這一點，事實上早有大量先例，例如中聯辦書店旗下三中商政治審查書籍等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果大家對中共這個最大最危險敵人坐視不理，任由他們在香港做大</span></strong>，取得主要市場佔有率，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真香港人將會面臨像澳門一樣既無野做（只有低級前線工作，而你上司係支那大學畢業講支那話既支那人）/無聲出（出聲即炒，唔跪即炒）既困境</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以我地必須<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正視中共經濟威脅，採取先紅後藍對策</span></strong>，立即採取以下行動，不得怠誤：<br />\n1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做好黃色經濟圈</span></strong><br />\n目標：打破中資壟斷、保手足就業、建立物資支援據點<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將抵制中國貨（Anywhere but China,簡稱ABC）推廣到全球</span></strong><br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將香港中資列表推/轉發到前線見到（見下面#2）</span></strong><br />\n只要大家做齊做好以上三點，我有絕對信心能夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">襯現時支爆以及中美貿易戰大環境，重創中國經濟，產生支爆，從而令支那人大量失業並進行革命，推翻支共。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"47245417eadee16e5adf05502582c6f66c03e17f","tid":1813233,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:28:07.000Z","msg":"中聯辦中資企業list:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.locpg.hk/jmwl/zgzjqy/zyzzqk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.locpg.hk%2Fjmwl%2Fzgzjqy%2Fzyzzqk&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=0fdf4059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.locpg.hk/jmwl/zgzjqy/zyzzqk</a><br />\n香港中國企業協會會員list:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcea.com/app2/#/sort_index?id=175&amp;title=會員展示\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcea.com%2Fapp2%2F%23%2Fsort_index%3Fid%3D175%26title%3D%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=9db06105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcea.com/app2/#/sort_index?id=175&amp;title=會員展示</a><br />\n以下是重點：<br />\n華潤集團（根正苗紅黨企）<br />\nPacific Coffee<br />\nVango<br />\n華潤萬家<br />\n華潤堂<br />\n<br />\n電訊<br />\n中國移動<br />\n中國聯通<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦書店<br />\n三聯<br />\n中華<br />\n商務<br />\n<br />\n銀行/保險<br />\n中國銀行<br />\n工商銀行<br />\n交通銀行<br />\n建設銀行<br />\n中信銀行<br />\n永隆（招商）<br />\n南洋（中國信達）<br />\n集友（中銀）<br />\n創興（越秀）<br />\n<br />\n香港四大國企<br />\n1. 中國港中旅集團公司 (香港中遊社、中旅汽車、)<br />\n連安信兄弟都係佢<br />\n2. 招商局集團有限公司 (招商銀行、招商局國際 、招商局置地)<br />\n3. 華潤（集團）有限公司 (華潤創業、華潤電力、華潤置地、華潤水泥控股、華潤燃氣)<br />\n4. 中國光大集團股份公司<br />\n<br />\n其餘在港國企<br />\n5. 中國電信<br />\n6. 中國聯合網絡通信<br />\n7. 中國移動<br />\n8. 華為<br />\n9. 中國工商銀行<br />\n10. 中國建設銀行<br />\n11. 中國建築<br />\n12. 中國農業銀行<br />\n13. 中國平安保險<br />\n14. 中國人壽保險"},{"pid":"27aa3a2ede155bd06b8a4b64dc36eb8fa38dbaf7","tid":1813233,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"原討論po，大家幫手推推<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4508a66f45652fd9898c2aa3b4919c6d801b70b0","tid":1813233,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:28:45.000Z","msg":"Download左和你Pay了，要養成習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f51e5661dc262ad960295326a3ada2da84bfca","tid":1813233,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:29:05.000Z","msg":"得閑大家幫我推埋兩個舊po<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n政府咁驚黃色經濟圈係因為......<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cda8f1dec8f41068a8a026539a07af1b49c92d08","tid":1813233,"uid":116331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:30:30.000Z","msg":"中共最鍾意全方位侵略<br />\n民生：日常消費唔同行業都插大支旗係到<br />\n人口：不斷送大陸「專才」同低等人口黎溝淡<br />\n經濟：不斷比「著數」你換你簽乜簽物<br />\n最後就會完全依賴中共，好似柬埔寨同其他東南亞小國咁"},{"pid":"dd8e2a9f18058befb9a99bf1262051a1883ed32d","tid":1813233,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黎明行動 不如驅蝗行動</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768351</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">發起普通話杯葛行動</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1781696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1781696</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3702d5543b427c1c3c516c6932a361d1dd3f15e","tid":1813233,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T19:47:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebfc24f2bd278734d7c610891ae636b8052d0280","tid":1813233,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4386fe56fac806202a776ce8b44707a64429800d","tid":1813233,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6785c26824ced73ec94e1d38fb0814889affffd","tid":1813233,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:50:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89e7e1649620a940497b6a3f1f6f86fc86bb4fe6","tid":1813233,"uid":24133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"樓上條五毛扮撚曬嘢推post <img src=\"/asset